<HEAD>Bangladesh Floods Threaten At Least 20 Million; Death Toll More
Than 1,000</HEAD>
<NOTE>Eds: SUBS 4th graf,`Dhaka newspapers ... million people.' to
UPDATE with disease deaths included in toll. Picks up 5th graf,
`The government ...'
^An AP Extra</NOTE>
<BYLINE>By EARLEEN FISHER</BYLINE>
<BYLINE>Associated Press Writer</BYLINE>
<DATELINE>DHAKA, Bangladesh (AP) </DATELINE>
<TEXT>
